# Build stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jdk-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
RUN mvn dependency:resolve

COPY src ./src
RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="analytics-team" \
      description="Java analytics dashboard" \
      version="1.0"

WORKDIR /app

# Install system dependencies for fonts and curl
RUN apk add --no-cache \
      fontconfig \
      ttf-dejavu \
      curl && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

# Import AWS RDS and Azure certificates
RUN apk add --no-cache ca-certificates && \
    wget -q -O /tmp/rds-ca.pem https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem && \
    wget -q -O /tmp/azure-ca.pem https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca -file /tmp/rds-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    keytool -import -alias azure-ca -file /tmp/azure-ca.pem -cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca.pem /tmp/azure-ca.pem

# Create non-root user
RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -u 1001 -G app -s /sbin/nologin -D app

# Copy application JAR from builder
COPY --from=builder --chown=app:app /build/target/app.jar .

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

ENTRYPOINT ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
